Tags:
  - Life-Love=The Primordial State=Purity, Simplicity, Wholeness
  - 197
By: Michael Sendivogius
---
Know for certain that Nature is wonderfully simple; and that the characteristic
mark of a childlike simplicity is stamped upon all that is true and noble in
Nature. If you would imitate Nature, you should take her simplicity for your
model in all the operations of Art.
